 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-height: 40vh;vertical-align: baseline\">","options":["<p>$2 \\, \\mathrm{ms}^{-2}$</p>","<p>$4 \\, \\mathrm{ms}^{-2}$</p>","<p>$10 \\, \\mathrm{ms}^{-2}$</p>","<p>$20 \\, \\mathrm{ms}^{-2}$</p>"],"answer":0,"solution":"","type":"mcq","questionType":"mcq","source":"ExamGoal JEE Main 2027","image":null,"_examgoalId":"tq-mr3c2pe4","_bank":"examgoal_2027"},{"id":4183822072,"subject":"Physics","chapter":"Laws Of Motion","q":"<p>Two blocks A and B with masses 4 kg and 6 kg respectively are connected by a stretched spring of negligible mass as in figure. When the two blocks are released simultaneously, the initial acceleration of B is $1.5 \\, \\text{m/s}^2$ westward. The acceleration of A is</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/6y3zli1mra265nm/b07792af-54c7-4409-a2ae-9dff46fe7b38/92ce3020-79af-11f1-9eb6-139adce7efb6/file-6y3zli1mra265nn.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/6y3zli1mra265nm/b07792af-54c7-4409-a2ae-9dff46fe7b38/92ce3020-79af-11f1-9eb6-139adce7efb6/file-6y3zli1mra265nn.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-height: 40vh;vertical-align: baseline\">","question":"<p>Two blocks A and B with masses 4 kg and 6 kg respectively are connected by a stretched spring of negligible mass as in figure. When the two blocks are released simultaneously, the initial acceleration of B is $1.5 \\, \\text{m/s}^2$ westward. The acceleration of A is</p>\n\n<img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/6y3zli1mra265nm/b07792af-54c7-4409-a2ae-9dff46fe7b38/92ce3020-79af-11f1-9eb6-139adce7efb6/file-6y3zli1mra265nn.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/6y3zli1mra265nm/b07792af-54c7-4409-a2ae-9dff46fe7b38/92ce3020-79af-11f1-9eb6-139adce7efb6/file-6y3zli1mra265nn.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width: 100%;height: auto;display: block;margin: 0 auto;max-heigh